name: Hella-Soul Shirt
description:
Started in 2011, Hella-Soul. Brings simplicity into reality. The term hella is used to greaten the impact of another word. (i.e. "that's Hella sick") "We say Hella" is our motto here at H.S. From your soul to your sole, we have found a way to keep your individuality original. 

    The Hella-Soul Shirt, is a shirt based off simplicity. It's that shirt you can pick up off the floor and rock to any casual event. The design is simple but still catches people's attention.

http://wesayhella.tumblr.com/



The grey and black shirts will have a white design.
The black shirts will have a black design.
